  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488050/extras/2022bff11143f9fd32eaf63902c60deb.avif?t=1772418372\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A neighboring country has declared war!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The first war in a long time. Due to a shortage of personnel, Estelle, the princess, has taken command of the army.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She can't afford to lose this war, but... What will she do, Estelle!?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488050/extras/2635ad886136ac558405685d7f9e0a20.avif?t=1772418372\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn-based strategy SLG. You move soldiers as units and battle with the enemy army. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Status bonuses are granted to soldiers who achieve military success. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you want more military funds, you can work part-time in the towns in your territory. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488050/extras/531fa923cf133c692d1e626e05b9729b.avif?t=1772418372\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn-based strategy SLG</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Main character fully voiced</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Auto-play function</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488050/extras/2022bff11143f9fd32eaf63902c60deb.avif?t=1772418372\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A neighboring country has declared war!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The first war in a long time. Due to a shortage of personnel, Estelle, the princess, has taken command of the army.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She can't afford to lose this war, but... What will she do, Estelle!?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488050/extras/2635ad886136ac558405685d7f9e0a20.avif?t=1772418372\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn-based strategy SLG. You move soldiers as units and battle with the enemy army. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Status bonuses are granted to soldiers who achieve military success. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you want more military funds, you can work part-time in the towns in your territory. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488050/extras/531fa923cf133c692d1e626e05b9729b.avif?t=1772418372\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn-based strategy SLG</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Main character fully voiced</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Auto-play function</p></li></ul>",
